VB 嘅廢老瓜晒之後，你真係屎都有得食，你試吓訪問吓啲年青啲嘅人，仲有幾多個會睇電視！<br />\n無創新，奶共，追唔上時代，先至致命！"},{"pid":"7dff4226d1990a886a098c2b7de7db423d82642b","tid":1786011,"uid":79161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0bcd69e47d004a0b4a75da17bd46fe2c38b6dd5","tid":1786011,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"00e93fa32ac40014e3dd41ec48c5e81632972d6f","tid":1786011,"uid":228143,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:00:14.000Z","msg":"2個深藍又互咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T00:06:36.000Z","msg":"佢又深藍?<br />\n定係嬲豬cctvb呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"太skr狗出哂名係五毛<br />\n係唔係都周圍屌"}]}